title: Flight Simulator 2020 - POI's - Canada -  Lethbridge Viaduct
description:
In this video we will fly over the Lethbridge Viaduct. The Lethbridge Viaduct, commonly known as the High Level Bridge, was constructed between 1907 and 1909 at Lethbridge, Alberta, Canada at a cost of $1,334,525.
